moji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:35:40.000Z","msg":"係架<br />\n耶穌降生係講福音，福音就係講悔改，悔改就係講因為一定會有審判同報應。<br />\n林鄭捐幾多錢都無用"},{"pid":"c5b7ef750a7350a0bc235482bb5e583122447fda","tid":1775963,"uid":69741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:52:30.000Z","msg":"推，應該襯聖誔新年鞏固黃圈<br />\n反而藍既就無錢賺"},{"pid":"e13649f9c1174226fcd5117d6fd051c9904154ab","tid":1775963,"uid":112081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:53:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b51b01f0d4c37615f6e1d3d161e7fd151b8f468","tid":1775963,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:54:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd834ac084eea836b2c3b2b2582cdeb608466622","tid":1775963,"uid":225977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bb65a459ba2005134937e4ec2b74d69b7a3d1e8","tid":1775963,"uid":80560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:11:16.000Z","msg":"聖誕有子夜彌撒，手足應該參加，塞爆教堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:55:07.000Z","msg":"去教堂記得要尊重人哋宗教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f2a5f828a3ee6408983b4f0dfc5a17367efaf5","tid":1775963,"uid":277873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd834ac084eea836b2c3b2b2582cdeb608466622","tid":1775963,"uid":225977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bb65a459ba2005134937e4ec2b74d69b7a3d1e8","tid":1775963,"uid":80560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:11:16.000Z","msg":"聖誕有子夜彌撒，手足應該參加，塞爆教堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:55:07.000Z","msg":"去教堂記得要尊重人哋宗教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T10:55:08.000Z","msg":"如果本身唔係教徒唔知去邊間，可以問吓啲黃絲教友先，費事唔小心入咗啲偏藍既教會聽完一肚火。不過有唔少教會其實都係又藍又黃（即係好似你一堆親戚咁都總有啲藍有啲黃），傳道人同幹事同會友都